                    <p>We know that you care how information about you is used and shared and we appreciate your trust in us to do that carefully and sensibly. This page answers some important questions about how we collect, use and protect your personal details. By visiting <a href="/">http://www.jisc-collections.ac.uk</a>, you are accepting and consenting to the practices described in this Privacy Notice.</p>
